dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents flood areas for Racine County, Wisconsin in 2003. This point data layer represents floods for Raceine County, Wisconsin in 2003. They are feature classes with in the geodatabase RacineCounty_Floods_2003.gdb. The dataset was originally published by the Racine County Public Works and Development Services in 2003.
